Veteran actor, Richard Mofe Damijo who recently turned 61 has left many celebrities in stitches as he shares a very hilarious and energetic video of himself and content creator, Frank Itom choreographing to a mixed tape.
Mofe Damijo who days ago, expressed his gratitude for the grace bestowed on him, has dropped this interesting dance video of himself vibing too energetically (considering his age) to a mix array of songs.
See the video here
The video captured the attention of many celebrities who absolutely loved the clip and wasted no time in pouring encomium on the veteran actor.
